title: Johnny Hates Jazz - Turn Back the Clock (1992)
description:
Turn Back The Clock is the debut album by Johnny Hates Jazz released in 1988. Led by vocalist Clark Datchler, JHJ were an instant hit with their slick hook-filled late '80s Pop, best experienced on this album, originally released in 1987. The album peaked at #1 on the UK charts, and #56 on the Billboard 200.

(Source: Wikipedia & Amazon.com)
